#

Zucchini Mozzarella Pizza Bites

$10.5
150 kcal
Difficulty: 30%

Allergens:

Dairy

Dietary Tags:

VegetarianLow-Carb

Tags:

AppetizerSnackHealthyCheesy

Description

Deliciously cheesy and savory, these zucchini bites are perfect for a healthy snack or appetizer!

Ingredients

  • Zucchini: 2 medium
  • Mozzarella cheese: 1 cup shredded
  • Parmesan cheese: 1/4 cup grated
  • Italian seasoning: 1 teaspoon
  • Garlic powder: 1/2 teaspoon
  • Olive oil: 1 tablespoon
  • Salt: to taste
  • Black pepper: to taste
  • Fresh basil: for garnish
